# 6. Plugin Manifest

ทุก Plugin ต้องมี

```yaml
id: worksheet-ai

name: AI Worksheet Generator

version: 1.0.0

sdk_version: 1.0

author: Example

license: MIT

category: content-generator

homepage: https://example.com

permissions:

- worksheet.generate

- ai.generate

events:

- content.resource.created

- ai.job.completed

routes:

- /generate

dependencies:

- ai-runtime

minimum_platform: 1.0

maximum_platform: 2.x
```

